{"tid":1211153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家可以轉用新嘅資訊整合溝通用平台—Discord","createTime":"2019-06-12T15:09:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T15:06:47.000Z","uid":5735,"like":30,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c0f7c14a374a7755faaab21925336cd279f4a3b9","tid":1211153,"uid":5735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:09:55.000Z","msg":"(啱啱開錯台唔好意思)<br />\n啱啱大家都應該知道telegram公海谷主畀人拉咗同埋俾大量黑客入侵緊既消息，telegram絕對唔夠安全同埋保密，同埋最重要係太多唔同嘅group令到所有人嘅資訊太過混亂，前線同埋後勤資訊無限重疊。Discord最好地方係<br />\n1)可以一個地方開幾個CHANNEL，唔洗分散幾十個GROUP 討論，同時可以切換版面睇唔同類型嘅資訊<br />\n2)可以分channel@分工合作，前線同埋後勤可以分開討論，可以及時提醒前線人員狗賊最新動態，同時又唔洗比物資內容洗版<br />\n3)同時可以控制權限，控制唔同人睇到嘅野，咁樣係確定個個人唔係狗賊嘅時侯先睇到多d資訊，唔係就淨係睇到公海資訊<br />\n4)discord唔洗大家留手機，開個垃圾email就可以，比較安全&nbsp;<br />\n5)最重要可以即時多人通訊，保持機動性，大家係撤退嘅時候可以保持通訊，唔駛各自跑。<br />\n6)最後係最危險嘅情況下谷主可以delete成個group，無人會查到。<br />\n<br />\n最後歡迎大家入group討論：<a href=\"https://discord.gg/t5KNQQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2Ft5KNQQ&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgvwexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=ea00315d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/t5KNQQ</a><br />\n<br />\nAndroid:<a href=\"https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/discord/id985746746%3Fmt%3D8&amp;ved=2ahUKEwio3MvkmuTiAhUotlkKHcYkD_kQFjABegQIBRAC&amp;usg=AOvVaw0YMYYLbiqr7eLknLeYorCd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26source%3Dweb%26rct%3Dj%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fdiscord%2Fid985746746%253Fmt%253D8%26ved%3D2ahUKEwio3MvkmuTiAhUotlkKHcYkD_kQFjABegQIBRAC%26usg%3DAOvVaw0YMYYLbiqr7eLknLeYorCd&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgvwexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=4d2e55c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/discord/id985746746%3Fmt%3D8&amp;ved=2ahUKEwio3MvkmuTiAhUotlkKHcYkD_kQFjABegQIBRAC&amp;usg=AOvVaw0YMYYLbiqr7eLknLeYorCd</a><br />\nIOS:<a href=\"https://www.go